School Closure Until Further Notice, Remote Learning starting on March 30th. 

Based on guidance from Weld County Health, the Colorado Department of Education, and the Governor’s office, Eaton School District will be closed until further notice. We will transition to Remote Learning starting on March 30th. Please contact your child's school for more information. Thank you for your support and understanding. 



 COVID-19 Community Resources 








Food Distribution During School Closure 

EVERY FRIDAY
9:00 am to 10:30 am
Galeton Elementary School parking lot
Eaton High School parking lot
Supplemental food packages are on a first come, first serve basis while supplies last. One per family.




